00:41:08.296 --> 00:41:10.586 A:middle
including the static analyzer

00:41:10.586 --> 00:41:13.346 A:middle
and auto layout warnings and the

00:41:13.346 --> 00:41:14.346 A:middle
new pseudo languages.

00:41:15.976 --> 00:41:18.636 A:middle
And then you can export your --

00:41:18.636 --> 00:41:20.136 A:middle
all your localizable content

00:41:20.136 --> 00:41:21.386 A:middle
into a single XLIFF.

00:41:21.836 --> 00:41:23.236 A:middle
