00:41:23.236 --> 00:41:24.666 A:middle
dict files, which are really

00:41:24.666 --> 00:41:26.536 A:middle
powerful for handling plurals

00:41:26.536 --> 00:41:27.616 A:middle
and adaptive strings.

00:41:29.036 --> 00:41:30.666 A:middle
And finally, when your XLIFF is

00:41:30.726 --> 00:41:32.676 A:middle
translated you can import it

00:41:32.676 --> 00:41:34.326 A:middle
back into your project and that

00:41:34.326 --> 00:41:36.026 A:middle
integrates the translations into

00:41:36.026 --> 00:41:37.496 A:middle
all the different pieces of your

00:41:37.496 --> 00:41:37.606 A:middle
app.

00:41:39.326 --> 00:41:40.656 A:middle
And then you can take advantage

00:41:40.656 --> 00:41:42.896 A:middle
